  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerReaction
    Class for representing answer reaction in the Tester.
    MaximizedImage
    This class is to make possible to see loaded picture in better detail, you can double click on selected image on the panel and this dialog will load image in resizable container, where you can "zoom" it as you need.
    Tester
    This Frame represents The Tester, which loads questions from file into array and randomly set questions to the end of the list.
